{"id": 239719928, "title": "Idanre community to honour Akinyelure, Akin Deko, Akintan, others", "text": "In recognition of their great contributions to the development of the ancient kingdom of Idanre, Ondo State, the Idanre Development Assembly is set to honour some prominent sons and daughters of the town at a grand reception and award ceremony. Among those to be honoured include the Chairman, Board of the Nigerian National Petroleum Company Ltd, Chief Pius Akinyelure; a retired justice of the Supreme Court of Nigeria, Samuel Akintan, as well as Omolara, the wife of a former Chief of Defence Staff, Alexander Ogomudia; as well as post-humous awards to a former Minister of Agriculture and former Lisa of Idanre Kingdom, Chief Gabriel Akin Deko; and a former Executive Director of Wema Bank, Prince Afolabi Ayinuola. The awards will be presided over by the Owa of Idanre, Oba Fredrick Aroloye; while the Ondo State Governor, Lucky Aiyedatiwa, will be one of the special guests. A statement issued by the President-General of IDA, Dr Anthony Omolola, and made available to Society Plus in Lagos, described Akinyelure as a distinguished technocrat with a proven track record in the oil and gas sector, as well as a seasoned administrator, businessman, foremost industrialist, philanthropist and astute politician. It added that the eminent jurist, Akintan, had an illustrious career, having risen through the ranks to serve on the Supreme Court between 2004 and 2008, when he retired, following which he served as a member of the Police Service Commission, and later the National Judicial Council for five years.", "summary": "<p>In recognition of their great contributions to the development of the ancient kingdom of Idanre, Ondo State, the Idanre Development Assembly is set to honour some prominent sons and daughters of the town at a grand reception and award ceremony. Among those to be honoured include the Chairman, Board of the Nigerian\u00a0 National Petroleum Company </p>\n <br/> <a href='https://punchng.com/idanre-community-to-honour-akinyelure-akin-deko-akintan-others/'>Read More</a>", "url": "https://punchng.com/idanre-community-to-honour-akinyelure-akin-deko-akintan-others/", "image": "https://cdn.punchng.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/23005317/Compress_20231204_105902_2194.jpg", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-06-23 00:06:23", "author": "Our Reporters", "authors": ["Our Reporters"], "language": "en", "source_country": "ng", "sentiment": 0.793}